platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Study thousands of stars, comets, and satellites with Fifth Star Labs’ stunningly gorgeous astronomy app. Using a built-in compass, Sky Guide lets you easily locate constellations and other celestial bodies—or you can simply hold up your device and learn more about what’s in front of you via dramatic photos and detailed descriptions. A stirring soundtrack and a time-lapse feature that shows where the moon and other objects will be later make your stargazing experience even more enchanting.
輕鬆定位星星、彗星、行星和衛星，你亦可以拿起你的裝置來了解面前的星體。澎湃的音樂和縮時攝影功能讓你的觀星體驗更加引人入勝。
宇宙广袤深远，星辰浩瀚无垠，你与它们隔着光年的距离，却又紧紧联系。举起设备，对准夜空，App 就能自动寻找恒星、彗星、行星和卫星。伴随着空灵悠扬的音乐，观星体验会更加迷人。

Easily locate stars, comets, planets and satellites – or you can simply hold up your device and learn about what’s in front of you. A stirring soundtrack and a time-lapse feature make your stargazing experience even more enchanting.
恒星や惑星、彗星や人工衛星を簡単に見つけることも、デバイスを頭上に掲げて、目の前の天体が何か学ぶこともできます。心に響くサウンドトラックやタイムラプス機能で、星空観察をより魅力的なものにしてくれます。

Easily locate stars, comets, planets, and satellites – or you can simply hold up your device and learn about what’s in front of you. A stirring soundtrack and a time-lapse feature make your stargazing experience even more enchanting.
你只要舉起裝置，這款 App 就能快速定位星星、行星、彗星與衛星，並提供優美的音樂與縮時功能，讓你的星空探索更加閃閃動人。

Localisez facillement des étoiles, comètes, planètes et satellites, ou laissez-vous surprendre en tenant votre appareil en l’air et en découvrant ce qui vous surplombe. La bande-son attrayante et la fonctionnalité de time-lapse vous permet de rendre encore plus enchanteresse votre observation du ciel étoilé.
